children.name: verify Job Search Result Using Different DataSet
And I enter title of job "Tester"
And I enter location "Harrow on the Hill"
And I click on More Search option link
And I select salary type "Per annum"
And I click on Find Jobs Button
Then I should see the message in result "Permanent Tester jobs in Harrow on the Hill"
